{"tid":675572,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要恰我地啲pt仔？","createTime":"2018-05-23T15:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T15:53:35.000Z","uid":21248,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3973f25c7fd73029be214b332760f2fbb363b23f","tid":675572,"uid":21248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T15:18:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟係台式連鎖飲品做pt<br />\n今日早少少嘅時候 就有對情侶嚟買嘢飲<br />\n一開口就同我個收銀同事講 俾前面2個大陸人打尖...etc<br />\n但個兩個大陸人一早行咗唔知去邊<br />\n我個同事新嚟無幾多日 又可能留意唔到唯有死哂狗咁話唔好意思<br />\n<br />\n條女全程閪撚哂面串柒柒 我心諗做乜鳩<br />\n你當下俾人打尖 連出聲捍衛自己嘅權利都唔識之餘 走嚟屌鳩我地啲打工仔 <br />\n因為知道自己係客大撚哂 覺得我地唔敢駁你所以就發洩係我地身上？欺善怕惡就係你呢種人<br />\n但真係啱嘅 我地呢啲半工讀嘅搵餐晏仔生活費真係唔敢屌你啲閪客 <br />\n<br />\n不過人都走撚咗你想我地點 <br />\n叫返個大陸人返黎重新買過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次如果人地留意唔到記得自己要出聲囉 人地絕對會幫你維護你嘅利益<br />\n尤其是對住啲大陸人 更加槍口一致對外<br />\n但連你自己都唔反抗 <br />\n而事後先嚟恰鳩啲新仔有咩用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就替你條仔可憐啦 要對住你啲咁嘅閪人<br />\n他朝有日可能俾人老強非禮都唔識反抗<br />\n事後走去屌自己男朋友唔好好保護自己<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就真係恭喜哂你"},{"pid":"00f738b570a2c732f71571a840273101d63b5ad2","tid":675572,"uid":116547,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"天生一對啦，做人條仔都唔敢岀聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n溝女喎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過香港係多仆街架啦"},{"pid":"374d28373dcd50f5021636a75e5ceb7a96ad131f","tid":675572,"uid":145731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"同樣台式連鎖飲品店<br />\n同樣遇唔少閪客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6db772b1d69b91f660656c9ed4a237386650e9","tid":675572,"uid":42049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T15:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我等巴士俾個阿婆打尖都唔敢出聲"},{"pid":"1911276ff8ca993c65e40bfdbf90d170d3b7fcdd","tid":675572,"uid":21248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00f738b570a2c732f71571a840273101d63b5ad2","tid":675572,"uid":116547,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"天生一對啦，做人條仔都唔敢岀聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n溝女喎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過香港係多仆街架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"仲要係廿零歲後生仔女<br />\n仲以為會明白事理啲<br />\n點知都係咁撚戇鳩"},{"pid":"9beb7e116780e9504280193efdae0c7654c2297b","tid":675572,"uid":21248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"374d28373dcd50f5021636a75e5ceb7a96ad131f","tid":675572,"uid":145731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"同樣台式連鎖飲品店<br />\n同樣遇唔少閪客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:00:07.000Z","msg":"真係做過服務性行業就知有啲香港人真係可以好撚仆街"},{"pid":"ad21a22f09fa50a7923b8638645eb4ea0fe440e9","tid":675572,"uid":21248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f6db772b1d69b91f660656c9ed4a237386650e9","tid":675572,"uid":42049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T15:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我等巴士俾個阿婆打尖都唔敢出聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:00:39.000Z","msg":"但你唔好屌鳩個司機就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a92eaa1e0fa94bd69db0d29950bb3da8e86f46","tid":675572,"uid":179333,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:09:00.000Z","msg":"D客最中意走住黎屌"},{"pid":"0850d8f5e9a8d5b94bb767a2b068653c8d5bd828","tid":675572,"uid":21248,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"19a92eaa1e0fa94bd69db0d29950bb3da8e86f46","tid":675572,"uid":179333,"like"